{"tid":1680894,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"費玉清告別演唱會 2019 香港站","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T11:11:13.000Z","uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"74911b9ae108f84df66a2b6ad4ae6ff3771d8a34","tid":1680894,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"2 Nov 2019 (Sat) 8:15 ‑ 11:15pm (3 hours)<br />\nHong Kong Coliseum 》9 Cheong Wan Road, Hung Hom, Hong Kong<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://timable.com/res/pic/e8106e4152c8e0af59a248001af15cac3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2Fres%2Fpic%2Fe8106e4152c8e0af59a248001af15cac3.jpg&h=ec998c37&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n寶島歌王費玉清即將告別樂壇，告別前嚟香港開一場紅館！<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊「我送你離開 千里之外 你無聲黑白」～<br />\n<br />\n沒有更好的方式，來感謝費玉清在樂壇的貢獻了！2019年11月2日晚，我們一起到紅館以最熾熱的掌聲，向小哥作最濃厚溫馨的回報，祝福他告別巡演後，有更豐富的人生！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無人買咗1280<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53bb09041b91a02ff88513c7bf16cfaaf18b68c","tid":1680894,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"廢肉ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129bc91b9b54a4242ccb79f78f7cd12766346913","tid":1680894,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ba339f79ce72587ae649506719e9903f4f581d13","tid":1680894,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f53bb09041b91a02ff88513c7bf16cfaaf18b68c","tid":1680894,"uid":206337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime